author: Richard G.
title: Richard G.
text: Ordered my first MTB with no problem it arrived to my door shortly after the designated time posted after order. I received some of the best fishing lures and baits for the month and it even came with sample hooks, tip booklet/digest, and sticker. Being that I subscribed to the basic Bass subscription I immediately upgraded to pro with one click and can't wait to receceive next months box because I know it will definitely be worth it! Thanks MTB! and anybody reading this go order your box now don't wait!
